Name: Slam Token
Description: It is a BEP-20 token on Binance Smart Chain. SLAM Token has and always will be the governance token of every platform under the SLAM Ecosystem. There is a 10% transaction fee to buy or sell $SLAM. 5% goes to the liquidity pool while other 5% is redistributed amongst SLAM holders.
